            <div class='text_wrapper'>
              <h2><a href="/articles/2013/02/14/2013-03443/assistance-to-states-for-the-education-of-children-with-disabilities">Assistance to States for the Education of Children With Disabilities</a></h2>
              <p class="metadata">
                A Rule by the <a href="/agencies/education-department">Education Department</a> on 
                <a href="/articles/2013/02/14"><date datetime="2013-02-14"><span class="date" datetime="2013-02-14">02/14/2013</span></date></a>
              </p>

              <p class="summary">The Secretary of Education amends regulations for Part B of the Individuals with Disabilities Education Act. These regulations govern the Assistance to States for the Education of Children with Disabilities program, including the Preschool Grants for Children with Disabilities program. </p>
            </div>
            <div class='bg'></div>

            
              <div class='attribution'>
                photo by: <a href="http://www.flickr.com/photos/47422005@N04/5790407340/lightbox">DonkeyHotey</a></a>
              </div>
              <div class='attribution bg'></div>
            

            <img alt="Navigation" src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/lede-photos.federalregister.gov/4138/navigation.jpg?1360842452" />
          </div>
        </li>
      
    </ul>
